                    ✨ Quality You Can Trust
                </span>
                <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white leading-tight mb-6 drop-shadow-sm">
                    Shop Fresh, Modern & Affordable Products
