                <p class="text-white/90 text-lg mb-8 max-w-lg leading-relaxed">
                    From household essentials to fashion gifts — delivered straight to your doorstep across Nigeria. Place your order and we'll confirm via WhatsApp.
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
                    <button class="h-13 px-8 bg-white text-brand font-extrabold rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors flex items-center gap-2">
                        Shop Now
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"></path></svg>
                    </button>
                    <button class="h-13 px-8 bg-transparent border-2 border-white text-white font-bold rounded-xl hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">
                        Track My Order
                    </button>
                </div>
                <div class="mt-10 flex items-center gap-6 text-sm font-medium text-white/80">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-white/20 flex items-center justify-center">📦</span>
                        <span>500+ Products</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-white/20 flex items-center justify-center">⭐</span>
                        <span>4.9/5 Rating</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="hidden lg:block relative h-[450px] bg-gradient-to-tr from-white/10 to-white/5 rounded-3xl border border-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm flex items-center justify-center shadow-2xl p-6">
